{"tid":1817060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武從來唔比文宣高級","createTime":"2020-01-08T17:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T18:20:23.000Z","uid":36489,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bcbc9d323d5e546a97feb68d6ceb7493a19bf2ef","tid":1817060,"uid":36489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"唔該啦！<br />\n<br />\n從來無勇武話自己比文宣手足高級。<br />\n<br />\n只不過文宣手足無俾同路人指控再被除罩影晒樣，之後被迫走佬，離開呢個付出一切去守護嘅家。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再放文宣手足上枱同退場嘅勇武比，大家諗下自殺，被自殺，失蹤，等緊打官司，被迫離開，準備入去坐嘅手足。我地應承左要代佢地走落去嫁，問下自己係咪有需要大愛到包容晒所有意見，問下自己有無其他角色可以繼續抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n唔好捉鬼，唔好退場，繼續抗爭啦屌你！<br />\n<br />\n我坐完都會繼續，就係咁！"},{"pid":"e86ef35fae5e243c010f78cbc62fcff4337b0b2f","tid":1817060,"uid":192824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:57:20.000Z","msg":"勇武退場，全香港人上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3a1d4ce1e1d5d655832ffa4fefb5905ede8ad7","tid":1817060,"uid":36489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86ef35fae5e243c010f78cbc62fcff4337b0b2f","tid":1817060,"uid":192824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:57:20.000Z","msg":"勇武退場，全香港人上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadbba302510269f989be06fd13cd566bc2e48e2","tid":1817060,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}